info.author: Kurt Schwehr
info.description:
These routines are written by Kurt Schwehr for various
        paleomagnetic processing and visualization jobs.  It is
        completely SEPARATE from Lisa's python routines.  It does
        depend on pmag >= 1.9 by Lisa Tauxe, which is her fortran
        packages that you can get from http://sorcerer.ucsd.edu/

WARNING: this code is just for my thesis.  Use at your own risk!
Please test and verify anything you might want to use on your own (and
then contribute those tests and documentation additions back to me).
I am sure there are errors in here.
